{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/Name.png?t=1736415008\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cRemote Reaper: FPV Drone\u201d is a simulator that immerses the player in the role of an FPV drone operator in the conditions of modern warfare. Strike enemy vehicles with FPV remote control drones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game offers realistic control using a controller, and simplified controls that allow you to control the drone using a keyboard and mouse easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each opponent's technique has vulnerabilities. Your task is to find these critical points and strike them with precision to destroy the enemy effectively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must perform various combat missions to destroy equipment, search, and strike from the air on important targets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in modern battles where the outcome depends solely on your skills and strategy. Accuracy and speed of reaction are key success factors, and well-thought-out tactics will allow you to dominate the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game world is based on the concept of modern warfare, where the latest military technologies are used. Combat vehicles and advanced drones play a crucial role in every conflict, allowing players to experience the real tension of military operations.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736415008","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736415008","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/99073bc4825d8032e46b5f3406b068fd94527239/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736415008","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea